<h1 id="filters">Filters</h1>

<p>Think of filters as playlists that collect your podcasts depending on conditions that youâ€™ve set. These conditions cover:</p>

<ul>
  <li>All podcasts</li>
  <li>Unplayed, In progress and/or played podcasts</li>
  <li>Podcasts release date</li>
  <li>Podcast download status</li>
  <li>Media type, either audio or video</li>
  <li>Podcast episode star status</li>
</ul>

