<h1 id="discover">Discover</h1>

<p>This tab contains the podcast directory, where podcasts can be searched and subscribed to. Itâ€™s organised into:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Featured</li>
  <li>Trending</li>
  <li>Popular</li>
  <li>Networks</li>
  <li>Category browser</li>
</ul>

