<h1 id="files">Files</h1>

<p>You can use Pocket Casts to listen to custom audio files such as audiobooks. You add these files by sharing them to the app from your devices files app. Subscribers to Pocket Casts Plus can upload the episodes to the cloud and access them on the go.</p>

<div class="media multiple">
    
        <img src="/assets/foto/varie/lazyload.png" data-src="/assets/foto/articolo/casts/files.jpeg" alt="" class="lazyload" />
        
        
