            <h3>Files and settings. </h3>
             
            <a href="/assets/foto/articolo/casts/files.jpeg">open image</a>
        </div>
        
</div>

<p>The files are supported by the audio effects just as well as normal podcasts episodes. I use this feature a lot as it enables me to listen to audiobooks via Pocket Casts.</p>

<h1 id="settings">Settings</h1>

<div class="media multiple">
    
        <img src="/assets/foto/varie/lazyload.png" data-src="/assets/foto/articolo/casts/general_and_appearance.jpeg" alt="" class="lazyload" />
        
        
