<h1 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h1>

<p>Pocket Casts is a great podcast app. It looks good, is packed with features, and is available on multiple platforms. And to top it all off, itâ€™s completely free! I got the app in 2016 and have been using it consistently ever since. Itâ€™s the most used app on my phone, and one of the first apps I download when I get a new phone. <a href="https://www.pocketcasts.com">Go try it out</a>, and see whether itâ€™ll change how you listen to podcasts.</p>

